list.name: Default
list.comment:
Removed Documentation + Removed RSA Encryption
The Files are now plain!

task.summary:
Small Fixes and Additions
- Changed CommonSprites Names for easier FightingClasses to Sprite Conversion - Minor bug fixes in RPGCharacter (not cloning stats) - Added HP and MaxHP stat - Added a nice character summary screen. - Minimised / Simplified the sprite loading in character creation.

Added the capability of running this in the terminal
You need to add the java parameter ``` -nogui ``` to the cmd.

Added Saving Capabilities
## RPGCharacter - Added xp and a basic algorithm to calculate level ups from xp - Aded conversion from and to JSONObjects
## Stats - Added conversion from and to JSONObjects
## Saves - read and write digitally encrypted and signed data
## HomeView - Added a Save and back to menu button
## LoadGameView - Displays Save Data ready to be loaded
## NewGameView - Fixed bug that Data would not be deleted if view was left (i.e. go back to main menu)
## RPGTests - Added a Test for JSON conversion
## StatsTests - Added a Test for JSON conversion
## pom - Added my libraries to the dependancy list
> Left warnings are produced by IntelliJ and mean nothing! > - PrinzJuliano

Moved Signition API
API works in IntelliJ but not as standalone!
